  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278230/extras/be1591ef0a7c6a914dda1d0edd19acad.poster.avif?t=1734953793\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278230/extras/be1591ef0a7c6a914dda1d0edd19acad.webm?t=1734953793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278230/extras/be1591ef0a7c6a914dda1d0edd19acad.mp4?t=1734953793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gravity Block 2 is a minimalist puzzle game where the player must control the environment to make the Block reach the end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use physics to your advantage and control the environment around the Block. Turn at the right time or you'll regret it!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 hand-crafted levels. From the simplest to the ones that will make you cry!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxing music (so you don't get even more irritated with the more difficult levels)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam achievements</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278230/extras/be1591ef0a7c6a914dda1d0edd19acad.poster.avif?t=1734953793\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278230/extras/be1591ef0a7c6a914dda1d0edd19acad.webm?t=1734953793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278230/extras/be1591ef0a7c6a914dda1d0edd19acad.mp4?t=1734953793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gravity Block 2 is a minimalist puzzle game where the player must control the environment to make the Block reach the end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use physics to your advantage and control the environment around the Block. Turn at the right time or you'll regret it!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 hand-crafted levels. From the simplest to the ones that will make you cry!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxing music (so you don't get even more irritated with the more difficult levels)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam achievements</p></li></ul>",
